REQUIREMENTS

CodeIgniter Version 2.0+

INSTALLATION

1. Copy all the files over to your existing installation.
2. Upload schema.sql to your database
3. Modify settings in config/database.php
4. Modify settings in config/tank_auth.php
5. Modify settings in config/tank_auth_social.php

